            <p class="text-base-600 text-sm">Each lesson covers both theory and practical work. Session length is tailored to your child's age and attention span.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-primary-100">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">ğŸ“</span>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-900 mb-2">Home-Based Studio</h2>
            <p class="text-base-600 text-sm">Lessons take place in Patricia's calm, comfortable home studio in Tengah, Singapore. House visits are available for families in Jurong West, Bukit Batok, Choa Chu Kang, and surrounding areas.</p>
